<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
    <meta name="theme-color" content="#000000" />

    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Roboto:wght@300;400&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />

    <style>
        body {
            width: 100%;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 10px 0px 10px 0px;
            line-height: 28px;
            font-family: Roboto;
            font-size: 18px;
            line-height: 27px;
            color: #4f4f4f;
            background-color: #E5E5E5;
        }

        table {
            margin: 0px auto;
            align-self: center;
            width: 700px !important;
            table-layout: fixed;
            border: none;
            background-color: #FFFF;
            border-spacing: 0pt;
            border-collapse: separate;
        }

        td {
            padding: 0;
        }

        .email-content {
            padding: 30px;
        }

        .title {
            font-weight: 700;
            font-size: 30px;
            line-height: 45px;
            color: #1a88c9;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            margin-top: 0px;
        }

        .greeting {
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }

        .fcx-img {
            width: 100%;
            max-height: 200px;
        }

        .sign-in-button {
            width: 180px;
            height: 44px;
            background-color: #1a88c9;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }

        .link {
            text-decoration: none;
        }

        .btn-text {
            color: #ffff;
            font-weight: 500;
            font-size: 16px;
            line-height: 20px;
        }

        hr {
            border: 1px solid #e2e2e2;
            margin: 0px;
        }

        footer {
            margin-top: 30px;
            font-weight: 400;
            color: #828282;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <table>
        <tbody>
            <tr>
                <td>
                    <header><img class="fcx-img" /></header>

                    <div class="email-content">
                        <h1 class="title">Hello world</h1>
                        <p class="greeting">Hi <span class="email">{{username}}</span>,</p>

                        <p>This is the message from the server to the user</p>
                        <p>It's time to wake up and go to the gym</p>
                        <p>Let us know you've done 100 push-ups and 50 sit-ups by submitting your info via
                            https://www.facebook.com/profile.php?id=</p>
                        <hr />

                        <footer>
                            <p>Stable Finance team.</p>
                            <p>This is an automated message, please do not reply.</p>
                        </footer>
                    </div>
                </td>
            </tr>
        </tbody>
    </table>
</body>

</html>